name: Atlas Air 747-4U7F Night Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Sorry for all the night videos lately. Winter sucks for spotting :(
Here we have an Atlas Air Boeing 747-400F landing at Calgary International Airport, arriving from Chicago-O'Hare. Fun fact: I caught this exact aircraft a few months ago landing on the same runway! Hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
